</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>BMW 推出全新電動車 iX3、i4 官方指為推出已接獲逾 700 訂單</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/06/bmw-ix3-i4/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=bmw-ix3-i4</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 05 Mar 2022 21:35:43 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[bmw]]></category><category><![CDATA[i4]]></category><category><![CDATA[iX3]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1089144</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>BMW 今天（3 月 4 日）正式發表全新電動車 i4 及 iX3，其中 i4 為 4 系 GranCoupe 的電動 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">BMW 今天（3 月 4 日）正式發表全新電動車 i4 及 iX3，其中 i4 為 4 系 GranCoupe 的電動版本，提供 i4 eDrive40、i4 eDrive40 M Sport Edition 及 i4 M50 三款選擇；</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">而 iX3 M Sport Edition 電動車則是建基於汽油版 X3。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089149" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.16-694x501.png" alt="" width="694" height="501" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.16-694x501.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.16-1247x900.png 1247w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.16-768x554.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.16.png 1336w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.19.37-694x455.png" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.19.37-694x455.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.19.37-1280x839.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.19.37-768x504.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.19.37-1536x1007.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.19.37.png 1540w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">i4 採用能量密度更高及容量達 80.7kWh 的鋰電池模組，BMW i4 eDrive40 採用後輪驅動後軸單摩打輸出配置， 340hp 的最大馬力輸出，0 到 100km/h 加速僅需 5.7 秒，峰值扭力達 430Nm，最高續航距離可達 590km； BMW i4 M50 則採用前後軸雙馬達四輪驅動配置，具備 544hp，峰值扭力達 795Nm，最大馬力表現，0 到 100km/h 加速更僅需 3.9 秒，最高續航距離高達到 510km。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089147" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.13.59-694x481.png" alt="" width="694" height="481" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.13.59-694x481.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.13.59-1280x888.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.13.59-768x533.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.13.59.png 1456w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089148" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.14.40-694x545.png" alt="" width="694" height="545" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.14.40-694x545.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.14.40-1146x900.png 1146w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.14.40-768x603.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.14.40.png 1266w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089150" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.56-694x483.png" alt="" width="694" height="483" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.56-694x483.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.56-1280x891.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.56-768x534.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.15.56.png 1466w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089151" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.26-694x486.png" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.26-694x486.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.26-1280x897.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.26-768x538.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.26.png 1456w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.49-694x486.png" alt="" width="694" height="486" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.49-694x486.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.49-1280x897.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.49-768x538.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.16.49.png 1456w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">全新 BMW i4 可以最高 200kW 的功率進行充電，透過高速充電站，只要充電 10 分鐘 i4 eDrive40 最多能補充 164km 的續航公里，而 i4 M50 則可達 140km 續航公里。原廠高壓電池更提供八年或十六萬公里保用。此外，全新 BMW i4 前軸與後軸位置加上專屬加固組件，而高壓電池外殼直接連接車架，加強車架剛性；另外後軸用上氣壓懸掛系統，不確保舒適乘坐體驗。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089145" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/P90423617_highRes_the-bmw-i4m50-6-2021-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/P90423617_highRes_the-bmw-i4m50-6-2021-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/P90423617_highRes_the-bmw-i4m50-6-2021-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/P90423617_highRes_the-bmw-i4m50-6-2021-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/P90423617_highRes_the-bmw-i4m50-6-2021-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/P90423617_highRes_the-bmw-i4m50-6-2021-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/P90423617_highRes_the-bmw-i4m50-6-2021-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">BMW iX3 搭載第五代 BMW eDrive 技術，配合 73.83 kWh 容量的鋰電池組及後驅電動摩打，可輸出最大馬力 286hp 及 300Nm 峰值扭力，0-100km/h 加速只需 6.8 秒，最高車速可達到 180 km/h。而 WLTP 測試標準下的最大續航里程高達 460 km，只需搭配 150kW 的直流電快速充電系統，則可於 34 分鐘內將電池充至 80%，即充電 10 分鐘可提供約 100 公里的續航力。若使用 11kW 的三相交流電快速充電，亦只需 7.5 小時完成充電。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.17.55-694x525.png" alt="" width="694" height="525" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.17.55-694x525.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.17.55-1189x900.png 1189w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.17.55-768x581.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/螢幕截圖-2022-03-04-下午 8.17.55.png 1358w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1089154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03